Basic Tests are mainly for 3 different part:
1. Royalty Split
    royaltySplit.test.js: Hierarchy tree structure for RAs and Individual accounts. Basic functions tests of royalty split machenism.
    royaltySplitUpdate.test.js: Complex functions of royalty split, including trouble shooting.
2. Stress Tests
    Stress test according to large batch size and depth of the hierarchy tree. Check the loading of the contract.
3. Transfer(both ERC20 & ETH)
    Token transaction and balance change in RAs and individual accounts, using both ERC20 token(supporting NFT trading and royalty) and ETH.

